items.title: 7 Children Are Killed in School Roof Collapse in India
items.description: An official in the northwestern state of Rajasthan said that heavy rain had pooled on the roof before it fell in.

items.title: Roof Collapse Kills 7 Schoolchildren in Northwestern India
items.description: A school roof fell in on Friday in Jhalawar, India, after heavy rains, killing seven children and injuring several others.

items.title: Thailand Warns of War With Cambodia as Deadly Clashes Enter 2nd Day
items.description: More than 100,000 people have been displaced in the deadliest conflict between the two nations in 14 years.

items.title: Russia Again Cuts Interest Rates as Its Economy Slows
items.description: Falling inflation has persuaded the central bank in Moscow to continue relaxing the country’s record borrowing costs.
